"""
============================================================================
 Cookie Run — Party Run FARM CORE (loaded after app login)
============================================================================
 This one file needs NOTHING else from the project - no other .py files,
 no creds.json, no descriptor files on disk. The gRPC protocol descriptors
 are embedded below (base64) and the descriptor pool is built in memory.

 What it does (pure Python, no device/emulator needed):
   1. Log in with your DevPlay email / password  -> game_access_token
   2. Clear any pending Party Run reward (claims it) so matchmaking is allowed
   3. RoomStream matchmaking (SOLO queue) -> get a live ingame session
   4. Connect to the ingame server, join, submit your run result
      (the server credits the coin / exp you send here)
   5. Quit to finalize instantly, then ClaimPartyRunReward -> rewards land

 Install:   pip install -r requirements.txt
 Usage:     python partyrun_single_file.py

 See README_partyrun.md for full documentation / troubleshooting.
============================================================================
"""

